OL,3,CPolice 'skivers' lose their jobs after
OL,4,Cprobe into GMP staff working from home
OL,6,FSix police staff have lost their jobs
OL,7,Fafter an investigation into skiving by
OL,8,Femployees working from home.
OL,10,FOne person was found to have bunked
OL,11,Foff for 84 hours.
OL,13,FThe move comes following a probe by
OL,14,FGreater Manchester Police into 'key
OL,15,Fjamming', where staff give the
OL,16,Fimpression they are working by placing
OL,17,Fan item on their computer.
