OL,3,CPolice 'skivers' lose their jobs after
OL,4,Cprobe into GMP staff working from home
OL,6,FAn operation by Greater Manchester
OL,7,FPolice's Anti-Corruption Unit has led
OL,8,Fto 28 police officers, civilian staff,
OL,9,Fand contractors facing formal
OL,10,Fmisconduct hearings.
OL,12,FThe hearings commenced this week and
OL,13,Fso far one has been sacked and five
OL,14,Fothers have resigned ahead of their
OL,15,Fhearing.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
