OL,3,CPolice 'skivers' lose their jobs after
OL,4,Cprobe into GMP staff working from home
OL,6,FThe force has chosen to go public with
OL,7,Fthe operation as a warning to others
OL,8,Fas part of an 'ongoing programme to
OL,9,Fdrive out poor performance and improve
OL,10,Fefficiency and effectiveness across
OL,11,Fthe force'.
OL,13,FThe six worked in a variety of
OL,14,Fdepartments across the force.
OL,16,FIt is believed thousands of working
OL,17,Fhours were lost by the behaviour of
OL,18,Fthe 28 investigated.
