OL,3,CPolice 'skivers' lose their jobs after
OL,4,Cprobe into GMP staff working from home
OL,6,FThree of the six would have been
OL,7,Fdismissed had they not already
OL,8,Fresigned.
OL,10,FThe force says working from home
OL,11,Fprivileges have been revoked while
OL,12,Finvestigations take place.
OL,14,FAdditionally, the line managers of
OL,15,Fthose involved will be spoken to 'and
OL,16,Fface greater leadership scrutiny'.
OL,18,FSince becoming Chief Constable in May
OL,19,F2021, Sir Stephen Watson has sacked
OL,20,F156 officers.
