OL,3,CPolice 'skivers' lose their jobs after
OL,4,Cprobe into GMP staff working from home
OL,6,FHe told the MEN: "GMP is determined to
OL,7,Fset the highest standards in policing
OL,8,Fbecause that is what the public and
OL,9,Fthe overwhelming majority of our
OL,10,Fworkforce rightly expects and
OL,11,Fdeserves."
OL,13,F"Since 2021, we have acted decisively
OL,14,Fto remove those who fall short, with
OL,15,F156 dismissals reflecting our
OL,16,Fcommitment to integrity and
OL,17,Faccountability."
