OL,4,Cprobe into GMP staff working from home
OL,6,FCommenting on the 'skivers'
OL,7,Finvestigation Deputy Chief Constable,
OL,8,FTerry Woods, said: "I'm grateful to
OL,9,Fthe work of the Anti-Corruption Unit
OL,10,Ffor conducting this proactive
OL,11,Foperation to root out poor
OL,12,Fperformance, dishonesty and conduct
OL,13,Fthat is just not conducive with
OL,14,Fworking for GMP."
