OL,6,F"This work is doing a great service to
OL,7,Fthe public and our workforce to ensure
OL,8,Fthat the people of Greater Manchester
OL,9,Fcan have confidence that their police
OL,10,Fforce will not stand for the tiny
OL,11,Fminority that reflect badly on the
OL,12,Fthousands of decent hard-working that
OL,13,Fserve the public so brilliantly every
OL,14,Fday."
