OL,3,CPolice 'skivers' lose their jobs after
OL,4,Cprobe into GMP staff working from home
OL,6,F"We're prepared to lead the way in
OL,7,Fproactively tackling police corruption
OL,8,Fand misconduct. As these recent
OL,9,Fproactive investigations demonstrate,
OL,10,Fthe Chief and I mean it when we say
OL,11,Fwe're serious about 'rooting out' and
OL,12,F'booting out'."
OL,14,FDetective Superintendent Simon Hurst,
OL,15,Fhead of the force's Anti-Corruption
OL,16,FUnit, said: "We have gone from being
OL,17,Freactive to intelligence about a
OL,18,Fcorrupt cop, to now looking under
OL,19,Fstones. It is a change in culture that
OL,20,FI am very proud of, and my team has
OL,21,Frisen to that change in culture."
